#### Description

This dashboard provides comprehensive visibility into audit activity within the Infoblox environment using the Infoblox integration. It offers an overview of key operational insights such as events categorized by Resource Type, Action, and Outcome, as well as user activity trends over time. Additionally, it highlights the top users, source IPs, and frequently accessed Infoblox resources, helping security teams monitor administrative behavior and support compliance and investigation efforts.
